Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电视上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:06.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在播放着相同的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:11.00,up,NTP,0,0,0,,目前  依然无法与新拜科努尔基地取得联系
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:15.16,up,NTP,0,0,0,,事故原因等具体消息依然尚不明了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.67,0:00:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事故发生后已经过去了半天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:23.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特的妈妈依然是生死不明
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据卫星拍摄的画面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个新拜科努尔基地都受到了爆炸的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前火势依旧凶猛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外  搭载在火箭上的实验堆也有可能发生了爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不排除有泄漏的可能
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说情况更加恶化了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.32,0:02:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然没有幸存者的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样  不仅仅是火箭爆炸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  会发生这种事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.33,0:02:36.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽是发生一些让我们束手无策的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.90,0:02:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这到底是为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么事情都是有可能发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.25,0:02:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到真的发生  没人能料到会发生怎样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.84,0:02:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经发生了的事情  是必定会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.67,0:02:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.17,0:02:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能被悲惨的现实击垮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坚信自己必能克服这样的悲剧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.10,0:03:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:07.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小库…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.42,0:03:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.49,0:03:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我全部都想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.36,0:03:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在牢房…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牢房？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.34,0:03:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静下来  库特莉亚芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.81,0:03:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的哦  小库
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.90,0:03:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都陪着你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.20,0:03:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天深夜  库特回了宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.81,0:03:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特没来上课
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.97,0:03:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们除了担心  无计可施
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭载在火箭上的实验堆爆炸了的可能性非常高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.45,0:04:10.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于担心存在泄漏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.47,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后可能将暂时关闭图布亚的边境
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.50,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说因为图布亚现在处在危险之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是进入还是离开图布亚都变得非常困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.35,0:04:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭里的机组人员是生是死  依然没有消息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.87,0:04:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小库她担心妈妈的安危  一定正坐立不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:38.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定  非常想飞回图布亚的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  现在无法进入图布亚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.52,0:04:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图布亚大使馆给了库特莉亚芙卡回国的机票
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子的母亲  在图布亚似乎是个非常有名的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此特许她的女儿回国
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:05:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是让她回去确认母亲是否平安
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说明天  大使馆的人就会来接那孩子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么库特她  要回图布亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:09.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在那里太危险了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能去了就再也回不来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.55,0:05:16.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  小库应该很想见自己妈妈的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.78,0:05:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小库的妈妈也一定安然无恙  正等着女儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.00,0:05:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小铃你也这么觉得的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.09,0:05:31.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的妈妈  已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:37.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算回去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定也只会留下…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:05:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是别回去好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.90,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤心的事情可怕的事情还是别看的好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特她太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Morning  错了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good Afternoon  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.72,0:06:20.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特  不用在意这个的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让大家担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起大家  现在库特和库特的妈妈才是更重要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你收到机票了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.59,0:06:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特你准备回图布亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.11,0:06:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想见妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:55.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却不能回图布亚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我来这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来日本…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是逃过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃过来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.13,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能听我说说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傻傻的我的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.61,0:07:22.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从小就非常憧憬妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.89,0:07:29.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然没跟别人说起过  我的梦想就是成为Cosmonaut
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库妮雅  你刚才说了什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想成为Cosmonaut  你是这么说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然也立志当宇航员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.56,0:07:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人高兴死了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.07,0:07:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特莉亚芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特莉亚芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为替你取了这个名字而感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一个进入宇宙的莱卡犬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小小的生命里蕴含着人类未来大大的希望哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特莉亚芙卡成为了这个世界里至关重要的一颗齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就和你的名字一样  成为世界里的一颗齿轮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有益于世界的一颗齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样在一年前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我进入了图布亚的航空学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,航空学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.60,0:08:28.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是训练Cosmonaut的专业机构
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了实现自己的梦想  发奋学习
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.09,0:08:38.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是比起预想  现实并没有那么顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.88,0:08:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在宇宙里必须会说英语和俄语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为上课用的是英语
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力就有回报什么的  根本就没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.69,0:08:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明妈妈那么天赋秉异
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.50,0:09:00.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女儿却是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.53,0:09:04.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经常被嘲笑我这是在浪费国家的预算
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都觉得我滑稽可笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么努力  依然是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得自己不是妈妈的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.96,0:09:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果只在学校呆了半年
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与妈妈不辞而别  我逃到了日本来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:41.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而在这里  我还是没什么出息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也不算  什么都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.07,0:09:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个对世界没用的废物齿轮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知妈妈对这么软弱的我会有多失望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不能回图布亚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特的软弱不是人皆有之的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.24,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃就像在听自己的故事般  一直低着头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特公还在犹豫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:24.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.77,0:10:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.63,0:10:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种复杂的事情我怎么会明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.28,0:10:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树  你多想想嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:36.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是最擅长思考了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.29,0:10:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得库特还是回去比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.76,0:10:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定很担心她妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是库特还没能整理好自己的思绪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.01,0:10:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果现在不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.81,0:10:59.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美女士肯定会后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.85,0:11:03.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许这辈子都见不到母亲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特莉亚芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.74,0:11:13.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起没去而后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是去了之后再后悔更好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不向前进  就得不到任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.51,0:11:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.04,0:11:24.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.73,0:11:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.86,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想留在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.18,0:11:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在大家的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会去给大使馆打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.67,0:11:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把机票还给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是库特做的决定  我们没资格去说三道四
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直在逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说飞起来  甚至连前进都做不到的库特莉亚芙卡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.22,0:12:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎已经想起所有事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又打算重复同样的时间  同样的经历吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.04,0:12:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能美你的愿望改变了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.26,0:12:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论能美你做什么选择
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理树以及我们都不会责怪你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.61,0:12:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  恭介同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.99,0:12:52.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介也认为库特应该回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.07,0:12:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对他人说「去勇敢面对痛苦」是很简单的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说说是很容易的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.86,0:13:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我没有坚强到能对库特说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.83,0:13:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论选择什么  最后剩下的只有后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.83,0:13:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的正确答案  根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杉并同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体不舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.32,0:13:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.88,0:13:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.25,0:13:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  修学旅行马上就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但一点都高兴不起来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三枝同学也肯定是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.25,0:13:49.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在活动室吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.15,0:14:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃  你肌肉不够哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呆站着干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个箱子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.02,0:14:22.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要准备烧掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.46,0:14:26.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这是值日生的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.70,0:14:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微…等下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:30.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用确认一下里面的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是不可燃垃圾就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊  有可能是食物啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.78,0:14:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是在库特房间里见过的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是库特扔的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.06,up,NTP,0,0,0,,这个真帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.65,up,NTP,0,0,0,,但是对肌肉好像没啥用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.35,up,NTP,0,0,0,,还没法吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.55,0:14:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么零件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狗牌…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:14:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是身份识别牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.03,0:15:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俄语
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库公打算把这么重要的东西烧掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.92,0:15:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个箱子可以先放在我这儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙开发史
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次世界大战后  最先发射人造卫星的是苏维埃联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:22.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乘坐斯普特尼克飞上宇宙的13只狗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:27.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.68,0:15:30.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,чернушка
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,英语是Blacky
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特的妈妈是黑头发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.56,0:15:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是她妈妈的身份识别牌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:45.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇宙工学概论
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,德维特和艾弗雷特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣埃克苏佩里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星之王子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.13,0:15:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个箱子里  满载着库特的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:01.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我证明了一下为什么天空是蓝的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好感动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.75,0:16:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾弗雷特的宇宙平行理论如果是正确的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.71,0:16:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这个世界上就会有无数个南十字星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直美妙到我快昏过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚我写了一篇关于黑洞和相对论的小论文
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为很难为情  所以没有告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.31,0:16:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你入学  库妮雅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.29,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.08,0:16:42.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是妈妈进入宇航局后一直在穿的披风和帽子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望它们能替我永远保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.95,0:16:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:16:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个帽子和披风
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你妈妈的东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.30,0:17:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如此重要的箱子  真的要丢掉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.09,0:17:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我梦想的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后悔的集合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.20,0:17:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经没有资格拥有它了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不适合做什么Cosmonaut
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.55,0:17:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.89,0:17:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特都没法抹消自己心中真正的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.54,0:17:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的想法？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.31,0:17:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特发自心底…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憧憬着宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.36,0:17:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必非要做到像你妈妈那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算很稚嫩  很笨拙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.02,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特只要寻找到自己力所能及的事情就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特只要做个像库特的齿轮  追逐宇宙之梦就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:15.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你憧憬的妈妈传达给你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.77,0:18:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特很想见妈妈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:29.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能逃避这种想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.97,0:18:33.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便被说成是胆小鬼又何妨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.85,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为库特最喜欢自己的妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会再逃避了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.67,0:18:46.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.59,0:18:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想见妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:56.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我想要去见她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.28,0:19:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这大概也是我想对自己说的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「不能逃避」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  理树
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机票带了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.24,0:19:20.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要小心点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特莱尔卡  威尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.00,0:19:47.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,铃同学
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.92,0:19:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特莱尔卡和威尔卡能拜托你照顾一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.99,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.51,0:19:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:19:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要听铃同学的话哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.48,0:20:01.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.04,0:20:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大使馆的人说了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.74,0:20:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我或许回不来日本了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.64,0:20:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:15.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约好了  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.74,0:20:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们等着你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.13,0:20:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来是能美…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是只有能美才能办到的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.88,0:20:38.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常在妈妈面前勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.17,0:20:41.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但其实那并不是真正的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论在何处  都会被人嘲笑成怪孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我总是孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.15,0:20:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在有了大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.85,0:20:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家接受了真实的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:58.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.06,0:21:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.23,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请念出「ни пуха ни пера」这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.68,0:21:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是祈求幸运的咒语哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.63,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泥噗喀…泥呸啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.09,0:21:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜了的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.60,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见  小库
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.30,0:21:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着你哦  能美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.88,0:21:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Прощайте
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.31,0:21:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对着重重困难
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.76,0:21:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特独自启程了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图布亚的情况超乎预想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.30,0:23:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回到祖国的库特迎来了荒谬的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.73,0:23:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只能祈祷她的平安吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.55,0:23:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,库特危在旦夕
